title: Known person
description: A natural person who has been identified, and information such as names, identifiers or biographical information can be provided about them.

title: Anonymous person
description: A natural person who has been identified, but identifying information is being withheld. The reason for non-disclosure should be given in the accompanying `unspecifiedPersonDetails` field.

title: Unknown person
description: A natural person whose identity has not been discovered or confirmed.
